title: Scottish independence referendum: Second vote to be called in weeks | Daily Star
text: BREAKING: Second Scottish independence referendum 'to be called in weeks' BREAKING: Second Scottish independence referendum 'to be called in weeks' A SECOND vote on Scottish independence will be called in weeks, a top Yes vote backer has said.
